JAVA STREAM (OBJECT BASED – IMPORTANT)

5. Given:

class Employee {
int id;
String name;
String dept;
double salary;
}

Q: Find highest paid employee per department
Answer:

Map<String, Optional> result =
employees.stream()
.collect(Collectors.groupingBy(
Employee::getDept,
Collectors.maxBy(Comparator.comparing(Employee::getSalary))
));

